column1: This file was created by CMPT_ME_PRIOR_RETS_DAILY using the 201509 CRSP database.
It contains value- weighted returns for the intersections of  2 ME portfolios
The portfolios are constructed daily.  ME is market cap at the end of the
previous day.  PRIOR_RET is from -  20 to -  1.
Missing data are indicated by -99.99 or -999.
